issue.title: I can't use optifabric with replaymod
issue.body:
### Describe the bug

The game is not loading 

### The log file and images/videos

[latestlog.txt](https://github.com/PojavLauncherTeam/PojavLauncher/files/13180871/latestlog.txt)


### Steps To Reproduce

```markdown
1. Start pojavlauncher
2. Install fabric version for 1.20.1
3. Download fabric api 0.90.4
4. Download replaymod 1.20.1-2.6.13
5. Copy and paste these mods in mod folder with optifabric and it's optifine i.e:OptiFine_1.20.1_HD_U_I5 and optifabric-1.13.25 
6. Total 4 mods installed
7. Set the renderer to ANGEL VULKAN 
8. Now Run the Fabric-0.14.24-1.20.1
```


### Expected Behavior

I expect the game launches without any problem for these mods 

### Platform

```markdown
- Device model: Samsung galaxy F23 5G
- CPU architecture: Qualcomm Snapdragon 750G
- Android version: Android 13(latest)
- PojavLauncher version: edelweiss
```


### Anything else?

_No response_
